Package: shared-mime-info
Version: 0.15
Revision: 1
Depends: libgettext3-shlibs, glib2 (>= 2.6.5-1), glib2-shlibs (>= 2.6.5-1), libiconv, popt-shlibs (>= 1.7-5), libxml2-shlibs (>= 2.6.19-2)
BuildDepends: glib2-dev (>= 2.6.5-1), pkgconfig, intltool (>= 0.33), libgettext3-dev, gettext-bin, gettext-tools, libiconv-dev, popt (>= 1.7-5), libxml2 (>= 2.6.19-2), libxml2-bin (>= 2.6.19-2), xml-parser-pm586
Source: http://freedesktop.org/software/%n/%n-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 51793b041edc68717c3f87e26a4bc087
SetCPPFLAGS: -no-cpp-precomp
ConfigureParams: --disable-update-mimedb --libexecdir=%p/lib/%n --mandir=%p/share/man --disable-dependency-tracking
InstallScript: make install DESTDIR=%d
RuntimeVars: <<
 XDG_DATA_HOME: %p/share
 XDG_DATA_DIRS: %p/share
<<
DocFiles: COPYING ChangeLog NEWS README
PostInstScript: <<
 export XDG_DATA_HOME=%p/share
 export XDG_DATA_DIRS=%p/share
 %p/bin/update-mime-database %p/share/mime
<<
Description: Shared MIME System
License: GPL
Maintainer: The Gnome Core Team <fink-gnome-core@lists.sourceforge.net>
DescPort: <<
 Added glib2-shlibs and libxml2-shlibs as Depends, and libxml2, 
 libxml2-bin as BuildDepends since otherwise it cannot be installed 
 with dpkg, hence impedes a lot of packages to be installed via dpkg.
 Modified by Michele Garoche.
<<
Homepage: http://www.gnome.org/
